flowchart LR
    A[Client Request] --> B[Attach Firebase ID Token]
    B --> C[Cloud Run API]
    C --> D[Auth Middleware verifyIdToken]
    D --> E{Valid token?}
    E -- No --> X[401 Safe Error]
    E -- Yes --> F[Zod Input Validation]
    F --> G{Valid payload?}
    G -- No --> Y[400 Safe Error]
    G -- Yes --> H[Business Logic + Quota Transaction]
    H --> I[External Calls GitHub/Gemini]
    I --> J[Schema Validation + Sanitization]
    J --> K[Persist to Firestore]
    K --> L[Safe JSON Response]
